lines.text: HOTEL/MOTEL RATES - FASEB CHICAGO MEETING - April 1-8, 1977
Note: The above rates are subject to an 8.1% City and State Tax.
If accommodations at the hotel/motel of your choice are not available the Housing Bureau will make
comparable reservations for you. If the requested rate is not available, the next available rate will be
assigned. You will receive confirmation direct from the hotel/motel assigned.
ALL CANCELLATIONS and CHANGES are to be made direct with the Hotel/Motel.
